mai (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging skeleton (SHIP-08).
  * mai-api systemd unit with ExecStartPre ship-validate gate.
  * Compliance dashboard unit (uvicorn + FastAPI).
  * Adapter manager unit (optional, started on demand).
  * mai-healthcheck.timer (5 min cadence).
  * postinst creates the mai system user, /var/lib/mai layout, and
    /etc/mai config tree with restrictive permissions.
  * prerm/postrm preserve customer data unless `--purge` is passed.

 -- Island Mountain <ops@islandmountain.io>  Sat, 23 May 2026 16:00:00 -0700
